THE HUNT

To install:
1. Fetch and install ncurses

    #apt-get install libncurses5-dev
    
    Or:
    
	ftp://ftp.gnu.org/pub/gnu/ncurses/ncurses-5.9.tar.gz	
	tar zxvf ncurses-5.9.tar.gz
	cd ncurses-5.9        
	./configure  
 	make
	su root
 	make install

2. make
3. ./hunt

Controls:

    W
A   S   D    

To attack/eat, just move the character in that direction.

To exit: Q

Enjoy the game!

